        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 13. Pentastiridus leporinus (Linnaeus, 1761). Specimens from Lugar de Baixo lagoon, 30 May 2004, on Phragmites australis Trin. ex Steud. A. Head, pronotum, and scutellum (dorsal view). B. Left paramere. C. Pygofer (left lateral view). D–E. Aedeagus (left and right lateral view). F–G. Anal tube (dorsal and left lateral view)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4663807/files/figure.png" .

